            <title><![CDATA[【图集】疫情受控下武汉市民迎接2021]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202101/20210101/2020-12-31t185037z_259292962_rc2iyk9jenvs_rtrmadp_3_health-coronavirus-newyear-wuhan.jpg?itok=3HqE1VOH" title="半夜钟声响起，大批武汉市民在江汉关大楼外释放气球，欢庆新一年的到来。（路透社）" alt src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202101/20210101/2020-12-31t185037z_259292962_rc2iyk9jenvs_rtrmadp_3_health-coronavirus-newyear-wuhan.jpg?itok=3HqE1VOH" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div><figcaption>半夜钟声响起，大批武汉市民在江汉关大楼外释放气球，欢庆新一年的到来。（路透社）</figcaption>

<p>大批武汉市民昨晚（12月31日）聚集在标志性建筑江汉关大楼外，准备迎接新的一年。半夜钟声响起后，现场民众释放手中的气球，直呼“新年快乐”。</p>

<figure class="image-placeholder"><img alt="china-health-virus-new_year-181339_Large.jpg" src="https://www.zaobao.com/sites/default/files/inline_images/20201225/china-health-virus-new_year-181339_Large.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><figcaption>大批戴着口罩武汉市民昨晚在户外欢庆新一年的到来。（法新社）</figcaption></figure><figure class="image-placeholder"><img alt="china-health-virus-new_year-181352_Large.jpg" src="https://www.zaobao.com/sites/default/files/inline_images/20201225/china-health-virus-new_year-181352_Large.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><figcaption>大批武汉民众在户外等待新一年的到来。（法新社）</figcaption></figure><figure class="image-placeholder"><img alt="china-health-virus-new_year-181405_Large.jpg" src="https://www.zaobao.com/sites/default/files/inline_images/20201225/china-health-virus-new_year-181405_Large.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><figcaption>大批武汉民众在户外等待新一年的到来。（法新社）</figcaption></figure><figure class="image-placeholder"><img alt="2020-12-31t172851z_1009195013_rc2hyk9yoohw_rtrmadp_3_health-coronavirus-newyear-wuhan_Large.jpg" src="https://www.zaobao.com/sites/default/files/inline_images/20201225/2020-12-31t172851z_1009195013_rc2hyk9yoohw_rtrmadp_3_health-coronavirus-newyear-wuhan_Large.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><figcaption>2021年降临后，武汉市民在江汉关大楼自拍。（路透社）</figcaption></figure><figure class="image-placeholder"><img alt="2020-12-31t170802z_1802308341_rc2hyk9fu5h9_rtrmadp_3_health-coronavirus-newyear-wuhan_Large.jpg" src="https://www.zaobao.com/sites/default/files/inline_images/20201225/2020-12-31t170802z_1802308341_rc2hyk9fu5h9_rtrmadp_3_health-coronavirus-newyear-wuhan_Large.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><figcaption>武汉公安一旁驻守，以维持秩序。（路透社）</figcaption></figure><p>武汉去年为了控制冠病疫情而“封城”了两个多月，疫情如今大致受到控制，但最近在中国多个城市通报的零星病例，提醒了武汉市民疫情仍未结束。</p>

<p>世界卫生组织专家小组定于本月抵达中国，以调查冠病疫情的起源。</p>
